WEBVTT

1
00:00:21.920 --> 00:00:25.600
THE 36TH CHAMBER OF SHAOLIN

2
00:02:42.360 --> 00:02:45.200
Good luck. General Yin.

3
00:02:50.160 --> 00:02:53.280
A man must do or die

4
00:02:53.400 --> 00:02:59.480
Mr. Ho. before I left.
Lord Cheng is concerned about you.

5
00:03:00.240 --> 00:03:03.560
If he can strike back with his army
and defeat the tartars. -

6
00:03:03.680 --> 00:03:06.240
credit for Canton will be yours

7
00:03:06.800 --> 00:03:10.000
One must sacrifice for one's country

8
00:03:11.600 --> 00:03:15.440
The 6 brothers arrested by tartars
Were tortured but have so far. -

9
00:03:15.560 --> 00:03:20.920
but refused to make a confession.

10
00:03:23.640 --> 00:03:24.520
This is most admirable

11
00:03:24.880 --> 00:03:27.360
If I failed.
I wouldn't even get arrested.

12
00:03:27.480 --> 00:03:31.000
General Yin.
- Mr. Ho. please.

13
00:04:01.880 --> 00:04:03.560
Sirs

14
00:04:04.840 --> 00:04:11.440
When Inspector-general.
And General Tien Ta arrive. -

15
00:04:12.680 --> 00:04:15.400
please say a good word for me.

16
00:04:15.520 --> 00:04:18.680
Don't worry. Mr. Magistrate.

17
00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:24.200
General Tien Ta ordered us
to capture the 6 traitors

18
00:04:24.320 --> 00:04:29.240
The Inspector Will supervise the execution

19
00:04:29.960 --> 00:04:30.960
Yes. yes...

20
00:04:31.080 --> 00:04:35.120
Tang San-yao. it's almost 12:30 p.m.

21
00:04:35.240 --> 00:04:37.880
Don't forget the General's command

22
00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:41.160
The Inspector-general is here!

23
00:04:41.680 --> 00:04:43.720
Make way...

24
00:05:39.240 --> 00:05:41.600
We're trapped!

25
00:05:42.160 --> 00:05:46.360
General Yin. I knew you'd be here
to "welcome" the Inspector-general.

26
00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:55.880
But he has not yet reached Canton!

27
00:06:15.480 --> 00:06:17.280
Stop!

28
00:06:18.920 --> 00:06:24.160
Your skill is comparable to a general.
Let's have a fair fight:

29
00:06:24.560 --> 00:06:30.160
A General to a General.
Let me try you out

30
00:06:30.280 --> 00:06:34.280
Good. I need a substitute.

31
00:07:41.920 --> 00:07:45.400
Let me fight you single-handedly

32
00:08:26.240 --> 00:08:28.200
Quiet down!

33
00:08:28.320 --> 00:08:32.360
The teacher's here...
The teacher's here. hurry up...

34
00:08:42.720 --> 00:08:44.000
Mr. Ho

35
00:09:11.360 --> 00:09:12.800
Mr. Ho

36
00:09:25.800 --> 00:09:28.440
Please have tea. Mr. Ho.

37
00:09:34.960 --> 00:09:37.360
Mr. Ho. why are you so late?

38
00:09:37.480 --> 00:09:40.800
Did you go to see the execution?

39
00:09:41.280 --> 00:09:42.880
Leave me alone!

40
00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:46.000
Executions should be interesting

41
00:09:46.120 --> 00:09:50.440
Lin Zhen. it depends on who it is.

42
00:09:50.560 --> 00:09:54.120
If it is the tartars who invaded us

43
00:09:54.240 --> 00:09:57.120
Of course it is interesting

44
00:09:58.040 --> 00:10:02.440
But today's convicts are patriots

45
00:10:02.560 --> 00:10:05.440
They are all Han's martyrs

46
00:10:05.560 --> 00:10:07.400
Do you still think it is interesting?

47
00:10:07.520 --> 00:10:08.880
I...

48
00:10:10.800 --> 00:10:14.960
Yesterday. I taught you sacrifice

49
00:10:15.080 --> 00:10:21.040
For the sake of a righteous cause
Do you all understand?

50
00:10:21.720 --> 00:10:23.040
Yes

51
00:10:25.360 --> 00:10:32.000
Hurry up... It's here

52
00:10:49.520 --> 00:10:51.440
Is he dead or alive?

53
00:10:51.560 --> 00:10:55.320
He's so stiff. of course he's dead.

54
00:10:59.440 --> 00:11:01.480
He's a hero

55
00:11:02.280 --> 00:11:04.200
What did you say?

56
00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:07.320
I...
- Capture him!  - Yes

57
00:11:08.280 --> 00:11:12.600
You're an accomplice.
- Lord Tang... Listen to me

58
00:11:12.720 --> 00:11:18.000
This student is not a bad man.
He's the son of a seafood shop owner

59
00:11:20.120 --> 00:11:23.760
Son of a shop owner?
- Yes. exactly.

60
00:11:23.880 --> 00:11:28.720
These are his classmates.
- Yes. we're his classmates

61
00:11:28.840 --> 00:11:30.960
Where are you studying?

62
00:11:31.080 --> 00:11:35.080
They all study in Chong Wen College

63
00:11:35.200 --> 00:11:39.000
Are you vouching for them. Mr. Wang?

64
00:11:39.120 --> 00:11:43.680
Yes. Apologize to Lord Tang

65
00:11:43.800 --> 00:11:45.120
I...

66
00:11:45.240 --> 00:11:50.360
You're too young and gauche.
Always causing trouble

67
00:11:53.400 --> 00:11:55.960
Do you know who I am?

68
00:11:56.080 --> 00:12:00.640
I do. Tang San-yao. Lord Tang.

69
00:12:04.240 --> 00:12:06.680
Yes. let's go. quickly!

70
00:12:08.520 --> 00:12:10.400
Uncle Wang. we didn't do anything!

71
00:12:10.520 --> 00:12:11.440
Yes. I know.

72
00:12:11.560 --> 00:12:15.400
Tang San-yao's notorious
for his craze after money and women

73
00:12:15.520 --> 00:12:19.160
You mustn't antagonize him.
As the saying goes:

74
00:12:19.280 --> 00:12:25.160
"One must humble oneself under enemy's rule"

75
00:12:34.520 --> 00:12:37.720
Mr. Ho... please open the door!

76
00:12:41.960 --> 00:12:43.360
Who is it?

77
00:12:48.160 --> 00:12:49.200
Mr. Ho

78
00:12:55.080 --> 00:12:56.760
Mr. Ho

79
00:12:59.080 --> 00:13:01.240
What's wrong?

80
00:13:01.360 --> 00:13:02.720
I...

81
00:13:03.120 --> 00:13:05.360
There's something we can't understand

82
00:13:05.480 --> 00:13:07.880
So we've come here even at this hour

83
00:13:08.000 --> 00:13:11.040
Humble oneself under enemy's rule

84
00:13:11.160 --> 00:13:15.560
Do we and our children have to
humble ourselves forever?

85
00:13:20.240 --> 00:13:25.640
I say. we'd be beheaded if we don't.
If we fear not death we don't have to

86
00:13:25.760 --> 00:13:29.000
You're right. It's well said

87
00:13:29.960 --> 00:13:32.880
One brave man alone is not enough

88
00:13:33.000 --> 00:13:36.200
But unity is strength

89
00:13:36.320 --> 00:13:40.320
The tartars are well-armed.
We...

90
00:13:42.040 --> 00:13:45.840
Men owes allegiance to his country

91
00:13:45.960 --> 00:13:48.600
Lord Cheng is recruiting in Taiwan

92
00:13:48.720 --> 00:13:52.680
He's become tartar's biggest trouble

93
00:13:53.040 --> 00:13:56.040
The Manchurian emperor has ordered -

94
00:13:56.160 --> 00:14:01.800
coastal residents to move away
and to be on their guard.

95
00:14:01.920 --> 00:14:05.720
Mr. Ho. I wish Lord Cheng could use us.

96
00:14:05.840 --> 00:14:10.320
The day will come.
Don't you all want to help?

97
00:14:10.440 --> 00:14:11.960
Yes

98
00:14:12.440 --> 00:14:15.120
Good. Come here.
- Yes

99
00:14:20.160 --> 00:14:24.160
Secret documents will arrive by sea

100
00:14:24.280 --> 00:14:27.920
I need a way to bypass customs.

101
00:14:28.040 --> 00:14:33.240
Liu Yu-de. doesn't your pa run
a seafood shop?  - Yes

102
00:14:43.800 --> 00:14:47.640
Open sesame...
- Shut sesame...

103
00:14:52.080 --> 00:14:55.520
Mr. Ho sent us here.
- Good

104
00:15:01.080 --> 00:15:03.920
Little brother. you're a brave fellow.

105
00:15:11.160 --> 00:15:13.000
Lock it up...

106
00:15:13.160 --> 00:15:14.880
Yes. hurry...

107
00:15:15.000 --> 00:15:18.280
Pa. has San Li's abalone arrived?

108
00:15:18.400 --> 00:15:19.720
The abalone... Go. go now!

109
00:15:19.840 --> 00:15:23.080
It has... The sea cucumber has too...

110
00:15:36.440 --> 00:15:39.240
Te. what are you doing?

111
00:15:39.920 --> 00:15:45.400
A big order for abalone was placed.
I am showing them some samples

112
00:15:45.520 --> 00:15:48.360
So you're in business now?

113
00:15:52.360 --> 00:15:57.000
Te. you can't take the whole case.
- I'm in a hurry to deliver it

114
00:15:57.120 --> 00:16:00.840
Hurry? Do you know the market price?

115
00:16:00.960 --> 00:16:05.080
The quality's high. Raise the price

116
00:16:06.520 --> 00:16:07.760
Open it.
- Yes

117
00:16:13.120 --> 00:16:19.080
Excellent kung fu.
- You'll find that at Shaolin Temple

118
00:16:21.760 --> 00:16:25.640
Mr. Ho. we could invite them to...

119
00:16:25.760 --> 00:16:27.960
Yes

120
00:16:28.960 --> 00:16:31.400
They don't involve in worldly matters

121
00:16:31.520 --> 00:16:34.440
If Shaolin taught kung fu to laymen -

122
00:16:34.560 --> 00:16:37.080
people could fight the tartars.

123
00:16:37.480 --> 00:16:39.640
That would be great!

124
00:16:56.120 --> 00:16:58.440
Yue Shan. South gate...

125
00:17:02.480 --> 00:17:03.920
Here

126
00:17:06.080 --> 00:17:09.120
General Tien
- Arise

127
00:17:10.000 --> 00:17:11.840
Come over here

128
00:17:16.760 --> 00:17:21.680
Lately. we've suppressed rebels -

129
00:17:21.800 --> 00:17:25.000
and found this on their leaders:

130
00:17:25.120 --> 00:17:28.200
Zheng Cheng-gong's edict

131
00:17:29.480 --> 00:17:32.000
Look. what have you been doing?

132
00:17:32.120 --> 00:17:38.640
There must be many of Cheng's men
hiding in Canton

133
00:17:40.280 --> 00:17:44.840
We must capture the rebels

134
00:17:47.480 --> 00:17:50.760
And kill them to scare them off

135
00:18:11.640 --> 00:18:17.360
Who's that?  - No idea.
He's secretive. maybe a spy.

136
00:18:17.480 --> 00:18:21.880
I'm innocent. I'm a delivery boy.
I've brought dried fish. Look!

137
00:18:22.000 --> 00:18:23.960
Shut up

138
00:18:43.880 --> 00:18:48.640
Lord Zheng. notorious rebels...

139
00:18:50.160 --> 00:18:53.680
Who told you to bring this here?

140
00:18:53.800 --> 00:18:56.360
No... no use to ask me

141
00:18:59.800 --> 00:19:04.120
Kid. we'll take you away

142
00:19:04.680 --> 00:19:08.920
And torture you one after another

143
00:19:09.760 --> 00:19:15.280
See if you'll talk or not.

144
00:19:17.080 --> 00:19:22.680
I'll talk... Don't torture me.

145
00:19:26.120 --> 00:19:35.160
I... I say. there is someone

146
00:19:43.040 --> 00:19:45.640
Go on with the torture -

147
00:19:54.480 --> 00:19:57.200
if you like!

148
00:20:11.840 --> 00:20:17.040
I saw a squadron of Ching troops
of over 100 patrolling our alley

149
00:20:17.720 --> 00:20:21.000
Mr. Ho. what shall we do?

150
00:20:22.040 --> 00:20:25.400
We must keep calm and be on the alert

151
00:20:25.520 --> 00:20:30.000
Yien-pin. let them hide in your home.

152
00:20:30.440 --> 00:20:32.880
Mr. Ho. what about you...?

153
00:20:35.320 --> 00:20:36.240
Mr. Ho. Mr. Ho

154
00:20:36.360 --> 00:20:39.080
Go quickly. go!  - What about you?
-Hurry up. quick

155
00:21:01.800 --> 00:21:03.720
Master. look!

156
00:21:03.840 --> 00:21:07.600
Please have mercy... please talk to them

157
00:21:07.720 --> 00:21:11.360
Please ask them not to...
- Quiet!

158
00:21:13.160 --> 00:21:17.200
General's order: No dried fish.

159
00:21:18.320 --> 00:21:19.960
Then...

160
00:21:23.440 --> 00:21:25.080
What's your relationship to Liu Yu-de?

161
00:21:25.200 --> 00:21:31.040
He... he's my son.  - Bring him here
- He's not home...

162
00:21:32.160 --> 00:21:36.240
Why do you want him?
- We've uncovered many spies recently

163
00:21:36.360 --> 00:21:39.200
One's a teacher; another's his pupil

164
00:21:39.320 --> 00:21:41.840
Liu Yu-de's a pupil of that school

165
00:21:41.960 --> 00:21:44.920
We'll capture him and torture him!

166
00:21:45.040 --> 00:21:48.560
Master. our young master won't...
Please have mercy

167
00:21:49.720 --> 00:21:53.840
How do you know he wouldn't?
- Let's talk it over

168
00:21:59.320 --> 00:22:02.720
Pa...
- Yu-de. run quickly... Yu-de

169
00:22:06.080 --> 00:22:08.040
Young Master. run. run quickly...
Run quickly. Young Master

170
00:22:08.160 --> 00:22:10.600
You want to rebel?

171
00:22:10.920 --> 00:22:12.600
Yu-de. run quickly. run!

172
00:22:38.640 --> 00:22:42.640
He's innocent! My son!

173
00:22:42.760 --> 00:22:44.840
Liu Yu-de. come up quickly!

174
00:22:45.400 --> 00:22:47.880
My son is innocent. my son!

175
00:22:58.080 --> 00:23:00.160
Change your clothes at once
- I...

176
00:23:00.280 --> 00:23:02.600
All wearing school uniform arrested

177
00:23:02.720 --> 00:23:06.120
Wonder what's happened to my home?
- Try to find a hiding place first

178
00:23:06.240 --> 00:23:08.960
We can find out later.
- Right. let's go now

179
00:23:16.240 --> 00:23:18.640
What has happened to my home?

180
00:23:18.760 --> 00:23:22.000
Your home...
- Tell me!

181
00:23:22.120 --> 00:23:27.120
All the houses in the street next
to your home have been cordoned off

182
00:23:27.240 --> 00:23:29.000
What about my father?

183
00:23:49.400 --> 00:23:50.600
Pa...

184
00:23:52.680 --> 00:23:56.520
Don't be sad. It's the same for mine

185
00:24:00.760 --> 00:24:03.640
I wish I had learned kung fu
instead of studying

186
00:24:03.760 --> 00:24:07.200
So I could fight them

187
00:24:09.680 --> 00:24:14.200
Studies teach us right from wrong

188
00:24:14.320 --> 00:24:19.160
What's the use of that?
We can't talk sense with the tartars

189
00:24:24.920 --> 00:24:27.320
We can't stay in this town anymore

190
00:24:27.440 --> 00:24:29.600
The martial arts headquarters is...

191
00:24:29.720 --> 00:24:32.160
Shaolin Temple

192
00:24:37.680 --> 00:24:40.320
We're lucky we made it

193
00:24:40.880 --> 00:24:43.480
Let's go straight on

194
00:24:50.440 --> 00:24:53.440
Did you see a group of men riding by?

195
00:24:55.920 --> 00:24:58.240
Why don't you answer me?

196
00:24:59.600 --> 00:25:00.880
Let's go!

197
00:25:16.720 --> 00:25:18.760
Dismount and chase them

198
00:25:19.440 --> 00:25:21.560
These two must be traitors

199
00:25:21.680 --> 00:25:24.280
One watch the horses. others chase

200
00:25:34.200 --> 00:25:36.120
Hurry up

201
00:25:47.080 --> 00:25:48.440
Let's go

202
00:26:07.800 --> 00:26:09.880
Liu Yu-de. mount it!

203
00:26:10.000 --> 00:26:11.720
Liu Yu-de?

204
00:26:12.520 --> 00:26:15.560
Liu Yu-de. escape now. Go!

205
00:26:15.680 --> 00:26:18.040
Don't let him get away

206
00:26:31.640 --> 00:26:34.280
Liu Yu-de. good luck!

207
00:28:30.240 --> 00:28:33.200
Please give me some water

208
00:28:56.720 --> 00:28:57.880
Thank you. uncle

209
00:28:58.000 --> 00:29:01.760
How far is it to Shaolin Temple?

210
00:29:01.880 --> 00:29:05.240
It's not far. only up the mountain.

211
00:29:05.360 --> 00:29:09.040
But you look like you can't make it.

212
00:29:09.160 --> 00:29:13.520
I can... even if I have to crawl there!

213
00:29:18.280 --> 00:29:19.640
Sit down.

214
00:29:21.880 --> 00:29:24.880
I don't think you can.

215
00:29:27.720 --> 00:29:33.800
Shaolin monks buy food here everyday

216
00:29:34.240 --> 00:29:37.080
Their cart is over there

217
00:29:46.240 --> 00:29:47.760
Hurry up... Do it orderly and quickly

218
00:29:51.800 --> 00:29:53.080
Get going. go!

219
00:29:54.640 --> 00:29:57.520
Why is it so heavy?

220
00:29:57.640 --> 00:30:02.640
Yes. I don't know why. Go.
You'll be punished if you're late.
Let's go. quick!

221
00:30:04.840 --> 00:30:09.200
Push harder. harder. go!

222
00:30:20.280 --> 00:30:22.800
Hurry up. park the cart there

223
00:30:23.560 --> 00:30:26.360
Come and lend a hand. everybody

224
00:30:26.480 --> 00:30:30.280
Why are you standing there. come here.

225
00:30:33.680 --> 00:30:36.600
Take this to the kitchen. Be quick.

226
00:30:44.400 --> 00:30:46.600
Why are you so slow?

227
00:30:47.560 --> 00:30:49.640
Hurry up...

228
00:31:03.520 --> 00:31:04.920
What's the matter?

229
00:31:05.240 --> 00:31:07.520
What's that man doing there?

230
00:31:10.960 --> 00:31:14.200
Stay calm. he can still be saved.

231
00:31:14.320 --> 00:31:17.320
Bring him inside. I'll tell the abbot

232
00:32:23.000 --> 00:32:27.080
Sir. the abbot would like to see you.
- Thank you

233
00:32:27.520 --> 00:32:31.120
This temple is not a sanctuary.

234
00:32:31.840 --> 00:32:35.080
You're spiteful and emotional.
Unfit to stay in the temple.

235
00:32:35.200 --> 00:32:41.120
You're recovering. please leave soon

236
00:32:46.280 --> 00:32:50.440
I had so much difficulty coming here.
I won't leave!

237
00:32:50.560 --> 00:32:54.640
Don't be rude.
- Splendid

238
00:32:57.680 --> 00:32:59.880
Since you are here...

239
00:33:00.000 --> 00:33:03.880
It means you've affinity with Buddha.

240
00:33:04.000 --> 00:33:07.560
Brother. you mustn't make exceptions.

241
00:33:08.440 --> 00:33:13.280
He arrived here in a coma.
but woke up after 10 days.

242
00:33:13.400 --> 00:33:19.400
Perseverance to Buddhism
warrants his admittance.

243
00:33:22.880 --> 00:33:26.360
Dharma also came to the east
with such perseverance -

244
00:33:26.480 --> 00:33:31.400
and laid the foundation of Shaolin.

245
00:33:37.120 --> 00:33:41.280
What are your opinions. brothers?

246
00:33:42.120 --> 00:33:44.760
You're right. brother.

247
00:33:48.120 --> 00:33:50.440
Thank you abbot.

248
00:34:33.560 --> 00:34:35.840
Morning. sir.

249
00:34:54.320 --> 00:34:55.600
San Te. San Te

250
00:34:57.880 --> 00:35:01.320
Morning. sir.

251
00:35:01.440 --> 00:35:06.240
How long have you been here?
- Over a year

252
00:35:06.360 --> 00:35:09.200
Are you unable to endure destitution?

253
00:35:09.320 --> 00:35:12.880
No. not that. but...

254
00:35:14.320 --> 00:35:17.840
Don't hide anything from the Buddha

255
00:35:20.800 --> 00:35:25.840
Before I came here. I heard Shaolin
is the headquarters of kung fu

256
00:35:25.960 --> 00:35:29.440
But for the past year. I've only cleaned

257
00:35:29.560 --> 00:35:32.720
I haven't seen any kung fu

258
00:35:33.160 --> 00:35:35.760
You can learn kung fu if you want to

259
00:35:35.880 --> 00:35:42.080
As long as they want to. any monk
can learn from the 35 chambers.

260
00:35:42.200 --> 00:35:46.280
If you don't tell us who would know?

261
00:35:46.800 --> 00:35:50.520
Why do you want to learn kung fu?

262
00:35:50.920 --> 00:35:53.360
Honestly. sir

263
00:35:53.480 --> 00:35:55.320
Before I came here. -

264
00:35:55.440 --> 00:35:59.120
I saw the people.
oppressed by tyrannical rule.

265
00:35:59.240 --> 00:36:04.240
If they were able to learn kung fu.
they could defend themselves.

266
00:36:04.360 --> 00:36:08.200
And combat enemies. Therefore...

267
00:36:08.720 --> 00:36:10.600
Good. good. San Te

268
00:36:16.200 --> 00:36:20.080
Buddhists shouldn't bear such thought.

269
00:36:20.200 --> 00:36:23.400
Don't mention it again!

270
00:36:23.520 --> 00:36:27.680
I won't be shaken.
I am determined

271
00:36:30.000 --> 00:36:34.680
Sir. can I still learn kung fu?

272
00:36:34.800 --> 00:36:39.240
There're 35 chambers in Shaolin.
Which chamber do you want to start?

273
00:36:39.360 --> 00:36:42.960
Which is the most advanced?

274
00:36:43.080 --> 00:36:44.760
The top chamber. of course!

275
00:36:44.880 --> 00:36:47.960
Then I'll start from the top

276
00:37:39.040 --> 00:37:40.280
Sir

277
00:37:40.400 --> 00:37:42.880
Behold. the Buddha says:

278
00:37:43.000 --> 00:37:45.680
Emptiness is the Eternal Five

279
00:37:45.800 --> 00:37:48.320
No sight. sound. smell. taste. sense.

280
00:37:48.440 --> 00:37:51.320
The five flavors dull the taste

281
00:37:53.520 --> 00:37:56.160
The five tones deafen the ear

282
00:37:58.160 --> 00:38:01.080
The five colors blind the eye

283
00:38:02.800 --> 00:38:06.000
It can also not be seen

284
00:38:06.880 --> 00:38:09.280
But it won't pass away

285
00:38:09.400 --> 00:38:10.920
Being at one is eternal

286
00:38:11.040 --> 00:38:14.000
But all things will come to you

287
00:38:15.040 --> 00:38:18.040
Without wisdom... without...

288
00:38:19.600 --> 00:38:20.960
Leave!

289
00:38:23.280 --> 00:38:26.000
No wisdom. no gain

290
00:38:26.120 --> 00:38:28.760
Gaining is not continuant

291
00:38:28.880 --> 00:38:31.560
All men will come to me one

292
00:38:31.680 --> 00:38:34.200
For there lies rest

293
00:38:34.680 --> 00:38:37.080
And happiness and peace

294
00:38:37.200 --> 00:38:40.000
It's invisible and inaudible

295
00:38:40.120 --> 00:38:42.960
And it's inexhaustible

296
00:38:43.320 --> 00:38:46.200
Can you hear the sound of bells?

297
00:38:46.320 --> 00:38:50.080
The heart is calm. We hear nothing

298
00:38:58.440 --> 00:39:02.560
How often do you recite the sutras?

299
00:39:03.240 --> 00:39:04.600
I... I...

300
00:39:07.120 --> 00:39:08.600
Go away!

301
00:39:08.720 --> 00:39:11.440
Sir. I came to learn martial arts.

302
00:39:11.560 --> 00:39:13.200
Get out!

303
00:39:20.600 --> 00:39:24.200
No one learns martial arts here

304
00:39:24.520 --> 00:39:27.080
This is the most advanced field

305
00:39:27.960 --> 00:39:30.960
You won't understand it

306
00:39:31.080 --> 00:39:34.240
I'm willing to start from the bottom

307
00:40:16.480 --> 00:40:20.760
Cross the pond to enter dining hall
- Yes

308
00:40:28.040 --> 00:40:30.720
Brother. this is the 35th chamber?

309
00:40:30.840 --> 00:40:35.120
Shut up. You starve if you're late

310
00:40:59.520 --> 00:41:02.960
Pure body is light. steps are stable.

311
00:41:03.080 --> 00:41:07.320
Don't enter the hall if you're dirty.

312
00:42:41.400 --> 00:42:43.920
How dare you enter this dining hall?

313
00:42:44.040 --> 00:42:47.440
Sir. I want to...
- Have congee?

314
00:42:52.600 --> 00:42:54.400
Come with me

315
00:43:10.640 --> 00:43:13.000
Stand on the wood

316
00:43:13.760 --> 00:43:15.320
Jump!

317
00:43:19.080 --> 00:43:20.880
Turn around!

318
00:43:24.440 --> 00:43:25.480
Eat!

319
00:43:53.000 --> 00:43:55.400
Get up. you're hopeless.

320
00:43:55.520 --> 00:43:58.360
Clean all the pottery and cutlery

321
00:44:45.840 --> 00:44:49.720
Wall is low. power of Buddha is high.

322
00:44:51.480 --> 00:44:54.560
He's fallen into it

323
00:44:56.520 --> 00:45:00.240
Don't laugh. he's only a novice.

324
00:45:01.360 --> 00:45:03.840
Enter the dining hall

325
00:46:30.520 --> 00:46:33.960
San Te. you're terrific...

326
00:47:05.720 --> 00:47:09.600
Concentrate. You'll find a way

327
00:47:09.720 --> 00:47:13.880
Keep practicing day and night. Go!

328
00:47:40.880 --> 00:47:42.520
Stop!

329
00:47:45.680 --> 00:47:50.280
Wood drifts. its buoyancy is limited.

330
00:47:50.400 --> 00:47:55.120
Harder you step. faster it sinks.

331
00:47:57.840 --> 00:47:59.280
San Te.  - Yes

332
00:47:59.400 --> 00:48:02.240
Throw the plate hard into water

333
00:48:07.080 --> 00:48:15.640
The plate sinks down in water
just like the wood you stepped upon.

334
00:48:24.920 --> 00:48:29.560
I keep the plate in motion. balanced.

335
00:48:29.960 --> 00:48:35.040
Similarly. step fast. balance body.

336
00:48:35.160 --> 00:48:39.320
Uniformity of mind
brings uniformity of maneuver.

337
00:48:39.440 --> 00:48:42.040
You must keep this point in mind

338
00:49:02.400 --> 00:49:06.560
Strength. balance. speed.

339
00:50:06.080 --> 00:50:10.480
Strength. balance. speed. Right

340
00:50:11.840 --> 00:50:14.800
Sir. I...
- Go!

341
00:50:16.720 --> 00:50:19.800
I beg you to teach me. master.

342
00:50:22.360 --> 00:50:26.320
34th chamber practice arms' strength

343
00:50:26.440 --> 00:50:31.880
Fist. palm. knife. sword. pole. spear

344
00:50:32.360 --> 00:50:36.280
All depend on arm strength. Look...

345
00:50:40.800 --> 00:50:42.840
This is the basic process:

346
00:50:42.960 --> 00:50:45.240
Carry the water up the slope

347
00:50:45.360 --> 00:50:50.760
Pour it down to keep it flowing.

348
00:50:51.600 --> 00:50:58.240
Remember. arms must be straight.

349
00:50:59.560 --> 00:51:06.320
You should carry water everyday
to build up arm strength. Go now.

350
00:52:56.280 --> 00:53:01.400
I didn't think you'd make it so soon.

351
00:53:05.800 --> 00:53:13.800
Don't help others when they practice.
It'll only ruin them

352
00:53:16.360 --> 00:53:19.400
You've violated our rule. Leave...

353
00:53:19.520 --> 00:53:24.520
Sir...
- Go to the 33rd Chamber

354
00:53:27.520 --> 00:53:29.440
Thank you. sir

355
00:53:30.600 --> 00:53:33.240
This chamber is comparatively easier

356
00:53:33.360 --> 00:53:36.160
Whenever you hear me knock the wood -

357
00:53:36.280 --> 00:53:39.640
Strike the gong.

358
00:53:45.360 --> 00:53:49.720
Sir. I'm here to learn kung fu. not...

359
00:53:49.840 --> 00:53:53.920
Don't little the bamboo poles. Ji Wei

360
00:54:01.960 --> 00:54:03.600
The hammer weighs 10 catties

361
00:54:03.720 --> 00:54:06.480
It is fitted into a 12-ft pole

362
00:54:06.600 --> 00:54:12.640
A 12-ft pole and 10-catty hammer
now weighs 120 catties

363
00:54:14.800 --> 00:54:18.520
How much can your wrists bear?

364
00:54:19.120 --> 00:54:22.280
I'm willing to try

365
00:54:37.320 --> 00:54:40.320
Add on 2 more feet

366
00:54:50.720 --> 00:54:52.360
Ready...

367
00:55:36.720 --> 00:55:39.240
Keep practicing

368
00:58:04.920 --> 00:58:07.480
My respects to the abbot

369
00:58:07.920 --> 00:58:15.440
You've left the Wrist Room?
- Yes. the overseer said I could leave.

370
00:58:16.360 --> 00:58:21.720
Good. Starting today...

371
00:58:21.840 --> 00:58:24.560
As a reward for your diligence

372
00:58:24.920 --> 00:58:27.680
You'll be in charge of Sutra Room.

373
00:58:27.800 --> 00:58:30.320
Thank you. abbot.

374
00:58:42.640 --> 00:58:48.120
Brother. San Te is ambitious

375
00:58:50.480 --> 00:58:53.360
He's not like our Buddhist brothers

376
00:58:53.480 --> 00:58:56.800
It's peaceful here in this temple

377
00:58:56.920 --> 00:59:00.960
But outside it's turbulent

378
00:59:01.080 --> 00:59:05.280
We may need someone like him

379
00:59:15.200 --> 00:59:18.400
Please guide me. sir.

380
00:59:22.760 --> 00:59:27.000
Stand between the two burning incense
- Yes

381
00:59:40.400 --> 00:59:48.600
Anyone practicing martial arts
must be sharp-eyed. Watch the lamp

382
01:00:02.200 --> 01:00:05.120
When the lamp oscillates...

383
01:00:05.240 --> 01:00:08.360
Your eyes should follow

384
01:00:08.480 --> 01:00:11.600
But remember

385
01:00:12.200 --> 01:00:16.320
Your head must not move.

386
01:00:19.560 --> 01:00:20.840
Start!

387
01:01:26.600 --> 01:01:30.360
Told you not to move your head.

388
01:01:31.040 --> 01:01:32.880
Again

389
01:01:55.720 --> 01:01:59.600
Right. the target has disappeared. -

390
01:01:59.720 --> 01:02:03.880
but still. the eyes shouldn't move.

391
01:02:06.600 --> 01:02:12.400
Eyes be bright. limbs be nimble.

392
01:02:13.080 --> 01:02:16.240
This is the way to do it
- Yes

393
01:02:22.520 --> 01:02:24.520
Turn around

394
01:02:47.200 --> 01:02:51.720
San Te. hit the reflecting blocks.

395
01:03:42.840 --> 01:03:48.200
You're my most outstanding pupil

396
01:03:49.800 --> 01:03:52.000
Thank you. sir.

397
01:03:52.880 --> 01:03:54.600
Head Chamber

398
01:04:26.240 --> 01:04:27.320
Continue

399
01:04:39.800 --> 01:04:42.760
Don't lower your head. Stand up

400
01:04:43.800 --> 01:04:47.240
Hands on your waist.
Use your head to hit the sand bags

401
01:04:47.360 --> 01:04:50.720
Then burn incense before the Buddha
- Yes

402
01:05:07.520 --> 01:05:08.840
Again

403
01:05:19.840 --> 01:05:21.240
Get up

404
01:05:21.360 --> 01:05:26.360
Sir. I...
- Collapsing so quickly?

405
01:05:27.440 --> 01:05:30.000
Get up now. Continue. Go on

406
01:06:02.880 --> 01:06:04.080
Sir

407
01:06:04.200 --> 01:06:07.040
San Te. Only after 2 years hard work -

408
01:06:07.680 --> 01:06:11.800
you might be able to enter this alley.

409
01:06:12.960 --> 01:06:16.640
San Te. head is the most important

410
01:06:17.360 --> 01:06:20.280
And the last phase in the training

411
01:06:20.400 --> 01:06:26.240
After going through it.
you can learn fighting and weapons

412
01:06:31.000 --> 01:06:33.200
Offer the incense

413
01:06:39.960 --> 01:06:44.000
Use your strength to hit it. Get up!

414
01:07:20.760 --> 01:07:23.840
You've set a new record

415
01:07:24.240 --> 01:07:32.560
You've completed the basic skills
of the 10 chambers in 25 months' time

416
01:07:33.160 --> 01:07:36.600
I can't do it without the teachers

417
01:07:36.720 --> 01:07:40.120
You can now practice boxing...

418
01:07:40.240 --> 01:07:46.040
Knife. baton and other skills
- Yes

419
01:07:47.320 --> 01:07:50.000
Justice Officer

420
01:07:50.120 --> 01:07:54.360
I'll make him head of Dharma House

421
01:07:58.280 --> 01:08:02.080
San Te. greet these two abbots.
- Yes

422
01:08:35.920 --> 01:08:38.400
Stop!

423
01:08:52.560 --> 01:08:54.320
Continue!

424
01:09:52.080 --> 01:09:53.800
San Te!

425
01:10:02.040 --> 01:10:03.760
Leg Chamber

426
01:10:19.680 --> 01:10:23.040
Sir
- San Te. not bad. not bad

427
01:10:28.320 --> 01:10:30.600
Sword Chamber

428
01:12:22.240 --> 01:12:24.640
Turn around faster

429
01:13:38.440 --> 01:13:40.760
Good fellow

430
01:13:56.360 --> 01:13:57.920
San Te

431
01:14:11.480 --> 01:14:16.440
San Te. it's commendable of you
to master all 35 chambers of kung fu...

432
01:14:16.560 --> 01:14:21.040
In only 5 years.

433
01:14:21.480 --> 01:14:29.960
Now I'll make you deputy overseer
of any of the 35 chambers

434
01:14:32.080 --> 01:14:36.200
Brother. San Te's post is high enough.

435
01:14:36.320 --> 01:14:39.200
He's been promoted 8 times in 5 years

436
01:14:39.320 --> 01:14:44.680
With his present skill he is
qualified to be deputy overseer

437
01:14:44.800 --> 01:14:47.960
Shaolin arts has existed for 1000 years

438
01:14:48.080 --> 01:14:51.520
We mustn't make a hasty decision

439
01:14:51.640 --> 01:14:54.560
In my opinion...

440
01:14:54.680 --> 01:14:59.040
Let him fight me with any weapon

441
01:14:59.160 --> 01:15:03.400
If he succeeds. he can be an overseer.

442
01:15:03.520 --> 01:15:07.120
You heard what he said

443
01:15:07.240 --> 01:15:11.160
What do you think?

444
01:15:12.960 --> 01:15:14.920
I dare not

445
01:15:16.120 --> 01:15:19.920
It's my idea. If you win...

446
01:15:20.040 --> 01:15:24.400
you can take charge of any chamber

447
01:15:24.960 --> 01:15:28.400
Excuse me then. sir.

448
01:15:53.600 --> 01:15:55.400
Watch out

449
01:16:32.840 --> 01:16:36.600
Thank you. sir. I've lost

450
01:16:39.280 --> 01:16:43.000
You may challenge me any time

451
01:18:27.800 --> 01:18:31.800
How many times have I tapped you?
- 17 times

452
01:18:31.920 --> 01:18:36.480
I could've hurt you with the blade

453
01:18:40.800 --> 01:18:42.680
You're right.

454
01:18:45.160 --> 01:18:48.200
I'll continue with my practice

455
01:18:51.840 --> 01:18:58.560
Brother. I think he'll never win.
- Not necessarily

456
01:20:25.960 --> 01:20:29.040
What weapon is San Te using?

457
01:20:29.160 --> 01:20:33.080
A two-jointed bar made by himself

458
01:21:07.240 --> 01:21:10.360
Good. that blow was not bad.

459
01:21:11.840 --> 01:21:13.400
Go on!

460
01:21:18.280 --> 01:21:20.600
Sir. are you alright?

461
01:21:20.720 --> 01:21:23.880
San Te. I still have my weapons.

462
01:21:54.080 --> 01:21:55.840
Excuse me

463
01:21:57.440 --> 01:22:03.080
Abbot. San Te can take
charge of any chamber.

464
01:22:03.200 --> 01:22:08.760
San Te. choose to take charge of
any of the 35 chambers...

465
01:22:09.440 --> 01:22:11.840
except the Top Chamber.

466
01:22:11.960 --> 01:22:16.920
Your Buddhism attainment is
not advanced enough

467
01:22:17.040 --> 01:22:21.560
Abbot. I've not yet made up my mind.

468
01:22:21.680 --> 01:22:24.520
Never mind. I'll give you 3 days

469
01:22:24.640 --> 01:22:27.400
Thank you. abbot.

470
01:22:28.600 --> 01:22:31.200
There're only 35 chambers in Shaolin

471
01:22:31.320 --> 01:22:33.200
There isn't a 36th chamber

472
01:22:33.320 --> 01:22:37.280
I know. I'd like to create it...

473
01:22:38.240 --> 01:22:39.760
This 36th chamber is...

474
01:22:39.880 --> 01:22:46.080
It's a pity Shaolin martial arts
is confined solely to the temple.

475
01:22:46.200 --> 01:22:49.640
It should be taught widely to all

476
01:22:50.400 --> 01:22:53.520
That's my idea for the new chamber

477
01:22:53.640 --> 01:22:58.200
To teach martial arts to laymen

478
01:23:01.440 --> 01:23:05.360
We don't involve in worldly affairs

479
01:23:05.480 --> 01:23:09.080
Nor do we admit secular pupils

480
01:23:09.200 --> 01:23:10.680
Forget it

481
01:23:10.800 --> 01:23:14.280
Abbot. this affects the handing down
of Shaolin martial arts to posterity.

482
01:23:14.400 --> 01:23:17.280
Please let me enroll promising youths -

483
01:23:17.400 --> 01:23:18.800
And train them in the 36th chamber.

484
01:23:18.920 --> 01:23:23.480
Nonsense. how dare you talk back?

485
01:23:27.600 --> 01:23:30.320
I don't mean to...
- Shut up!

486
01:23:30.440 --> 01:23:32.360
I must ask you to reconsider. abbot.

487
01:23:32.480 --> 01:23:34.720
Justice Officer

488
01:23:35.160 --> 01:23:41.120
Our pupil San Te should be punished.
- Yes

489
01:23:46.720 --> 01:23:49.880
San Te. you've violated our rule.

490
01:23:50.000 --> 01:23:53.680
You have to collect contributions

491
01:23:54.040 --> 01:23:56.520
Don't return unless the book is full.

492
01:23:56.640 --> 01:24:01.280
Yes. Abbot. I deserve punishment

493
01:24:02.440 --> 01:24:05.440
Leave tomorrow morning

494
01:24:49.200 --> 01:24:56.240
You want to pray for Chiang Tai?
They all died

495
01:24:56.360 --> 01:24:59.480
They were buried in East cemetery

496
01:24:59.600 --> 01:25:02.640
Go there and pray for them

497
01:25:12.000 --> 01:25:15.440
Uncle Wei. may you rest in peace

498
01:25:15.560 --> 01:25:20.000
We will complete your mission

499
01:25:20.120 --> 01:25:23.520
Hung Hsi-kuan. I knew you'd be here
to bury your accomplices.

500
01:25:23.640 --> 01:25:25.440
Run!

501
01:25:28.280 --> 01:25:31.200
Go! See how you can escape.

502
01:25:31.600 --> 01:25:35.680
Good! I'll kill you one after another

503
01:25:37.120 --> 01:25:39.800
Go ahead and try.

504
01:26:23.640 --> 01:26:26.280
Tang San-yao. you're so malicious.

505
01:26:26.400 --> 01:26:31.400
Your vice will be punished.
- Scram. bloody monk.

506
01:26:31.520 --> 01:26:33.360
Master. please stay out of this.

507
01:26:33.480 --> 01:26:36.000
So you're an accomplice

508
01:26:43.440 --> 01:26:45.960
Tang San-yao.
remember 7 years ago -

509
01:26:46.080 --> 01:26:51.160
you confiscated my school and my
shop and killed my whole family?

510
01:26:51.920 --> 01:26:56.400
You're Liu Yu-de. a fugitive!
Get him!

511
01:26:59.760 --> 01:27:03.280
Go help your brothers.
- Okay!

512
01:28:36.440 --> 01:28:39.680
You're a Buddhist. show mercy.

513
01:28:40.160 --> 01:28:43.200
Even Buddha has to conquer evil

514
01:28:43.320 --> 01:28:45.800
A monk should not kill

515
01:28:45.920 --> 01:28:50.200
A monk cannot but I can.
I'll do it!

516
01:28:54.120 --> 01:28:57.440
Tang San-yao. you've killed my men

517
01:28:57.560 --> 01:29:00.600
I'll stab you 1.000 times!

518
01:29:04.600 --> 01:29:06.880
Amitabha Buddha

519
01:29:16.000 --> 01:29:22.800
Thank God. Today. our martyrs
can see you lying dead here

520
01:29:24.760 --> 01:29:31.440
Master. I want to learn martial arts.
Please accept me as your pupil

521
01:29:33.640 --> 01:29:40.160
Good. I've come from Shaolin
to enroll promising youths

522
01:29:41.440 --> 01:29:45.960
Hsi-kuan. is Tien Ta still in Canton?
- Yes

523
01:29:47.080 --> 01:29:51.280
His hand is stained with Han's blood

524
01:29:52.120 --> 01:29:57.960
We must eliminate him at all costs

525
01:29:59.040 --> 01:30:01.160
We'll plan well.

526
01:30:01.480 --> 01:30:04.880
Find a hideout first.
Don't act rashly

527
01:30:05.000 --> 01:30:08.440
Do you know of other ambitious youth?

528
01:30:08.560 --> 01:30:12.520
Yes. Tung Qian-jin is another

529
01:30:13.520 --> 01:30:17.360
Tung Qian-jin. Commander's orders:

530
01:30:17.480 --> 01:30:20.040
Make a batch of wheels

531
01:30:26.680 --> 01:30:31.440
Deliver them within one month.
- I can't. it'll take one year.

532
01:30:31.560 --> 01:30:35.080
One year? Are you turning me down?

533
01:30:37.120 --> 01:30:40.040
Do you want to join the dead?

534
01:30:40.160 --> 01:30:42.360
Want my help?

535
01:30:46.880 --> 01:30:49.640
I'll teach you to be smarter

536
01:30:55.360 --> 01:30:57.200
Beat him up!

537
01:31:08.480 --> 01:31:11.080
Are you going to do it or not?

538
01:31:11.200 --> 01:31:14.080
Not over my dead body

539
01:32:00.560 --> 01:32:03.600
It is better to use the haft

540
01:32:46.520 --> 01:32:47.880
Help!

541
01:32:50.640 --> 01:32:53.160
Do you still want the wheels made?

542
01:32:53.280 --> 01:32:57.280
No. no!  - Damn you!
- Good! Good!

543
01:33:02.720 --> 01:33:04.680
Master. Master!

544
01:33:14.280 --> 01:33:19.520
Master... Let me follow you.

545
01:33:21.200 --> 01:33:22.120
Why?

546
01:33:22.240 --> 01:33:25.920
I admire you. Please teach me.
Please take me as your pupil

547
01:33:27.800 --> 01:33:29.960
Tung Qian-jin. what's wrong with you?

548
01:33:30.080 --> 01:33:33.840
You said you won't admire anyone
and will challenge even the Gods?

549
01:33:33.960 --> 01:33:38.680
Why are you kneeling to a monk now?

550
01:33:40.160 --> 01:33:44.000
What do you know? He's not a monk

551
01:33:44.120 --> 01:33:46.760
He's a Bodhisattva

552
01:33:46.880 --> 01:33:48.560
He only said several words

553
01:33:48.680 --> 01:33:51.400
and I scared the tartars away.

554
01:33:52.640 --> 01:33:55.960
So he's a living Bodhisattva?

555
01:33:56.080 --> 01:34:00.040
I'm only a monk from Shaolin Temple

556
01:34:01.600 --> 01:34:05.800
I taught you to avoid direct contact

557
01:34:05.920 --> 01:34:08.880
They've learned kung fu. you haven't

558
01:34:09.000 --> 01:34:15.160
Using a heavy weapon slows you down
And puts you at a disadvantage.

559
01:34:15.260 --> 01:34:20.880
- Right.
Lu Ah-cai. are you convinced now?

560
01:34:23.760 --> 01:34:26.600
Master. it makes sense.

561
01:34:36.400 --> 01:34:39.120
Lu Ah-cai. can you move?

562
01:34:46.960 --> 01:34:49.320
Lu Ah-cai. don't make hasty moves.

563
01:34:49.440 --> 01:34:52.520
Master. I'm convinced.

564
01:34:59.000 --> 01:35:02.040
Master. I'm convinced.

565
01:35:02.160 --> 01:35:05.560
Are you sure now?
- I am. I'm convinced

566
01:35:06.440 --> 01:35:09.800
Master. please come in for some tea.

567
01:35:40.280 --> 01:35:43.960
Master. I'm really convinced.

568
01:35:51.200 --> 01:35:56.400
How did Tang San-yao die?

569
01:35:56.880 --> 01:35:59.680
You still haven't found out yet?

570
01:35:59.800 --> 01:36:01.880
He was chopped by a knife

571
01:36:02.000 --> 01:36:03.680
I only want the man who chopped him.

572
01:36:03.800 --> 01:36:06.040
Yes. we're investigating

573
01:36:07.080 --> 01:36:11.320
Kill all suspects!
- Yes

574
01:36:17.120 --> 01:36:20.840
You must be on alert.

575
01:36:23.300 --> 01:36:24.220
Yes

576
01:36:25.640 --> 01:36:28.600
This is General Tien Ta's residence

577
01:36:28.720 --> 01:36:31.840
He patrols the city every day

578
01:36:31.960 --> 01:36:37.440
And he must pass through this street
when he goes to the city gates.

579
01:36:38.080 --> 01:36:46.040
Shops on both sides of the street
made it difficult for us to get him

580
01:36:52.280 --> 01:36:55.880
Any households on this street?
- Yes

581
01:36:57.920 --> 01:36:59.120
There is a rice-miller's shop

582
01:36:59.760 --> 01:37:02.560
Back to back with General's residence

583
01:37:02.680 --> 01:37:07.000
Are there many people living there?
- There seems to be only one person

584
01:37:29.520 --> 01:37:30.960
Sir...

585
01:37:37.000 --> 01:37:41.360
No one comes for offerings this late

586
01:37:41.480 --> 01:37:44.520
What are you doing? Go away...

587
01:37:52.400 --> 01:37:54.600
What do you mean by that?

588
01:38:00.880 --> 01:38:04.200
Sir. please excuse me.

589
01:38:04.520 --> 01:38:06.320
What do you want?

590
01:38:07.080 --> 01:38:09.480
May I know your name. sir?

591
01:38:12.160 --> 01:38:15.280
My father died
without telling me my name.

592
01:38:15.400 --> 01:38:17.600
So I have no name

593
01:38:17.720 --> 01:38:20.120
I started milling rice when I was six

594
01:38:20.240 --> 01:38:24.400
So they call me Miller Six

595
01:38:24.520 --> 01:38:31.480
I'm San Te. I'm from Shaolin Temple
- People say that monks from Shaolin...

596
01:38:31.660 --> 01:38:35.840
Are excellent at kung fu. No wonder...

597
01:38:35.960 --> 01:38:38.920
I've practiced for several years

598
01:38:39.440 --> 01:38:44.160
Having milled rice for many years
I also have a pair of strong feet.

599
01:38:47.800 --> 01:38:51.600
Do you want to try them?

600
01:39:04.200 --> 01:39:09.560
I've drunk a bit too much today.
But your footwork's not bad

601
01:39:10.320 --> 01:39:13.120
Let's go in for a drink. Let's go!

602
01:39:13.600 --> 01:39:17.960
You can't stay here much longer.
- Why not?

603
01:39:18.080 --> 01:39:24.920
Very soon. something big will
happen in the General's residence

604
01:39:31.440 --> 01:39:32.680
What is it?

605
01:39:33.160 --> 01:39:36.520
General Tien Ta's going to die here

606
01:39:37.680 --> 01:39:42.320
How can you say something like that?
You aren't afraid of being executed?

607
01:39:42.680 --> 01:39:45.240
Leave here at once. will you?

608
01:39:45.360 --> 01:39:48.640
I don't care whether you come from
Shaolin or Linshao Temple

609
01:39:48.760 --> 01:39:50.960
Please just leave. I beg you.

610
01:39:51.080 --> 01:39:54.080
Ching tartars killed so many people

611
01:39:54.200 --> 01:39:57.160
Don't you want to fight back?

612
01:39:57.280 --> 01:40:02.160
I'm only a rice miller. Even if I do...
What can I do?

613
01:40:02.280 --> 01:40:04.240
I'd rather drink

614
01:40:05.240 --> 01:40:11.120
People continue to suffer because
too many people have that attitude.

615
01:40:11.240 --> 01:40:14.040
You'd put it more plainly

616
01:40:14.160 --> 01:40:16.720
I want to borrow your place

617
01:40:16.840 --> 01:40:20.920
No... If you do...
I won't be able to stay here anymore.

618
01:40:21.040 --> 01:40:24.320
Don't worry. I'll take you to Shaolin

619
01:40:52.440 --> 01:40:56.960
Lord Cheng. we caught them
near the cemetery.

620
01:40:57.080 --> 01:40:59.400
Kill them all!  - Yes

621
01:40:59.520 --> 01:41:00.720
Stop!

622
01:41:03.680 --> 01:41:07.880
Lord Cheng. I killed Tang San-yao.

623
01:41:09.160 --> 01:41:11.040
Not them!

624
01:41:11.360 --> 01:41:12.800
You?

625
01:41:13.840 --> 01:41:17.840
How did you kill him?

626
01:41:24.320 --> 01:41:25.800
With this

627
01:41:25.920 --> 01:41:28.000
Take him!  - Yes

628
01:41:41.560 --> 01:41:44.080
Where did you learn it?

629
01:41:44.200 --> 01:41:46.640
In Shaolin Temple

630
01:43:27.680 --> 01:43:30.720
Report to the General! Quick!
- Yes

631
01:44:24.280 --> 01:44:29.880
Master. we're outnumbered.
- Yes. there're so many of them.

632
01:44:30.000 --> 01:44:33.280
Everyday they wake me up early

633
01:44:35.360 --> 01:44:37.920
Will you please calm down?

634
01:44:38.040 --> 01:44:41.320
No. I can't. I'm Miller Six

635
01:44:45.480 --> 01:44:47.680
This is flour

636
01:44:49.680 --> 01:44:53.520
Commanders Tang and Cheng are famous

637
01:44:53.640 --> 01:44:56.080
They failed because of...

638
01:44:58.600 --> 01:45:02.800
If more monks are here

639
01:45:02.920 --> 01:45:06.840
There will be a rebellion in Canton!
- Yes...

640
01:45:08.280 --> 01:45:12.560
I'll bring some men to capture him.

641
01:45:13.160 --> 01:45:17.160
Even if I have to go to Shaolin!

642
01:45:29.480 --> 01:45:33.520
Go. go at once... Run!

643
01:46:27.600 --> 01:46:30.080
Give me a sword

644
01:46:47.720 --> 01:46:51.600
You. a monk. joining the rebels!

645
01:46:55.960 --> 01:47:01.160
A Buddhist has to conquer evil.
How many lives have you taken?

646
01:47:01.280 --> 01:47:05.880
I've killed many. but never a monk.

647
01:50:03.880 --> 01:50:05.600
Stop!

648
01:50:34.160 --> 01:50:36.480
Twist and turn around!
